This template was designed to be used in creating well-formated lists of links in footer navagation boxes with adjacent items set apart by mid-dots (or other separators). 

Its key feature is that individual items which contain spaces will ''not'' end up broken between two lines and hence become harder for the reader to recognize. Rather, line breaks will only occur immediately after the separator.

