==Usage==
 <nowiki>
 {{WrapItemsAfterSeparator}}
 | title =
 | separator = 
 | item1 | item2 | item3 | […] }}
</nowiki>
All parameters are optional. 

The list of un-named parameters should not contain line-breaks, and its pipe-signs should have exactly one space on each side.<br />
The title will appear at the start of the list, emboldened, and will be followed by a colon and spaces.<br />
The separator defaults to a middot.

Equals signs in parameter values should be escaped as {{tl|Equals}}. (Not as {{tl|Eq}}, or as {{tl|{{Equals}}}}).<br />
Pipes in parameter values can be left as they are when they are used to create piped links. Otherwise they should be escaped as {{tl|!}}.

There is currently a limit of about 400 items: any more are silently ignored.

==Examples==
The basic usage, and probably most useful, is simply a list of items, which will normally be links, marked off by the pipe symbol (<tt>|</tt>), with ''exactly one space, and no carriage returns'', on each side of it.

